things started to grow dark and the walls around them and the open seemed physcadelic. and then it all went black.. he then held his arms out to the side and light flushed around him spinning like wind balancing light and dark his brilliant blue eyes turned a deep dark blood red;<br>
<br>
He stated something in a dead language.  and the reflection of himself appeared in the churning water standing still. not bothered by the movements of the water, And then the reflection began to change into something more dark and vile than even himself, and he spoke to mahrain telepathically.<br>
<br>
~ I can't stay here forevre mahrain, I hate that youve grown attatched to me, I hate that you don't care what I am. However, this might change that.... I hate that I've grown rather attatched to you.~<br>
<br>
A wall spoke up as it was splashed with a bit of water. &quot;He's at it again?&quot; The count smiled and told them to be quiet. Everything stopped and swven suddenly collapsed in the water, dissappeared. unless you looked below the surface.<br>
